k4me3 = pd.read_csv("./Brain-H3K4me3.TSS.mtx",sep="\t",skiprows=1,header=None)

group_boundary = [0,33913,34960,39731,41544]

labels = ['FSM', 'ISM', 'NIC', 'NNC']

# 
categories = []
for i, (start, end) in enumerate(zip(group_boundary[:-1], group_boundary[1:])):
    categories.extend([labels[i]] * (end - start))

k4me3["type"] = categories

p6 = pd.DataFrame()
for label in labels:
    t1 = k4me3.query('type==@label')
    t1 = t1[t1.columns[6:606]].mean(axis=0).to_frame()
    t1.index=range(1,601)
    t1["label"] = label
    p6 = pd.concat([p6, t1])
#     break

# p6.reset_index(drop=True).reset_index()

p6 = p6.reset_index()

p6.columns

# p6["index"] = p6["index"].astype('str')

p6.columns = ["index","value","label"]

plt.figure(figsize=(4,3))
sns.lineplot(data=p6,x="index",y="value",hue="label",palette=my_pal[:4])
plt.xticks(ticks=[0,300,600],labels=["-3 Kb", "TSS", "+3 Kb"])
plt.xlabel("")
plt.ylabel("Normalized H3K4me3 signal")
plt.savefig("/home/zhaoying/workbai/NC/Figure1/H3K4me3.pdf")
plt.show()

k27ac = pd.read_csv("./Brain-H3K27ac.TSS.mtx",sep="\t",skiprows=1,header=None)
# group_boundary = [0,33831,34878,39645,41454]
group_boundary = [0,33942,34989,39764,41577] 
labels = ['FSM', 'ISM', 'NIC', 'NNC']
# 
categories = []
for i, (start, end) in enumerate(zip(group_boundary[:-1], group_boundary[1:])):
    categories.extend([labels[i]] * (end - start))
k27ac["type"] = categories
p6 = pd.DataFrame()
for label in labels:
    t1 = k27ac.query('type==@label')
    t1 = t1[t1.columns[6:606]].mean(axis=0).to_frame()
    t1.index=range(1,601)
    t1["label"] = label
    p6 = pd.concat([p6, t1])
#     break
# p6.reset_index(drop=True).reset_index()
p6 = p6.reset_index()
p6.columns
# p6["index"] = p6["index"].astype('str')
p6.columns = ["index","value","label"]

plt.xticks(ticks=[0,300,600],labels=["-3 Kb", "TSS", "+3 Kb"])
plt.xlabel("")
